item.title: What's Going On With Alli & Bri?
item.description:
Welcome to Offscript! Get to know your hosts, Alli and Bri, as they share personal insights every week into their lives while exploring the dynamic relationship between books and their movie adaptations.  

Mondays bring you our main event – comparison episodes where we dissect the nuances between beloved books and their cinematic counterparts... Feed: https://feeds.redcircle.com/c2e8be73-3198-42f0-be1b-0efeaf97ca5b
